  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938460/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765099602\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938460/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765099602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938460/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765099602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Masterchef Chinese Food Edition is an exciting fast food simulation game. You just opened a chinese restaurant, let's see how fast you can satisfy your customers<br><br>Even if you're not a chef, with this game you will learn step by step very fast how to do your favorite chinese food like noodles, dumplings and more.<br><br>Game Features:<br>- More than 100 combinations to prepare the dishes<br>- 5 types of chinese food to choose to prepare: noodles, dim sum, dumplings, spring rolls and fortune cookies<br>- Strive to make good food every time so that you can consume it in the end",
